Package: SpinneR
Title: An Asynchronous CLI Spinner for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Skander", "Tahar Mulder", , "skander.tm@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a simple `with_spinner()` function to display a non-blocking,
    asynchronous spinner in the CLI while evaluating R expressions. The spinner
    runs in a background process using semaphore-based inter-process communication
    for clean resource management.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/skandermulder/SpinneR
BugReports: https://github.com/skandermulder/SpinneR/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    tools
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
SystemRequirements: C++11
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
